      h1 Nick Niles
      p.
        I'm a digital product designer and speaker with 20 years’ experience helping multinational corporations and small business reach their goals through thoughtful user-centered design. 
        
      p.
        With my background in digital design and Masters degree in Film Directing from Columbia University, I enjoy telling stories through motion graphics, animations, and rich interactive experiences. 
        
      p.
        I’m especially interested in the power of high-fidelity interactive prototypes to help teams save time and money.

